  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0001",
          "zh": "韓子曰：「儒以文亂法，而俠以武犯禁。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0002",
          "zh": "二者皆譏，而學士多稱於世云。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0003",
          "zh": "至如以術取宰相卿大夫，輔翼其世主，功名俱著於春秋，固無可言者。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0004",
          "zh": "及若季次、原憲，閭巷人也，讀書懷獨行君子之德，義不茍合當世，當世亦笑之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0005",
          "zh": "故季次、原憲終身空室蓬戶，褐衣疏食不厭。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0006",
          "zh": "死而已四百餘年，而弟子志之不倦。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0007",
          "zh": "今游俠，其行雖不軌於正義，然其言必信，其行必果，已諾必誠，不愛其軀，赴士之阸困，既已存亡死生矣，而不矜其能，羞伐其德，蓋亦有足多者焉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0008",
          "zh": "且緩急，人之所時有也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0009",
          "zh": "太史公曰：昔者虞舜窘於井廩，伊尹負於鼎俎，傅說匿於傅險，呂尚困於棘津，夷吾桎梏，百里飯牛，仲尼畏匡，菜色陳、蔡。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0010",
          "zh": "此皆學士所謂有道仁人也，猶然遭此菑，況以中材而涉亂世之末流乎？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0011",
          "zh": "其遇害何可勝道哉！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0012",
          "zh": "鄙人有言曰：「何知仁義，已饗其利者為有德。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0013",
          "zh": "故伯夷丑周，餓死首陽山，而文武不以其故貶王；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0014",
          "zh": "跖、蹻暴戾，其徒誦義無窮。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0015",
          "zh": "由此觀之，「竊鉤者誅，竊國者侯，侯之門仁義存」，非虛言也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0016",
          "zh": "今拘學或抱咫尺之義，久孤於世，豈若卑論儕俗，與世沈浮而取榮名哉！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0017",
          "zh": "而布衣之徒，設取予然諾，千里誦義，為死不顧世，此亦有所長，非茍而已也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0018",
          "zh": "故士窮窘而得委命，此豈非人之所謂賢豪閒者邪？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0019",
          "zh": "誠使鄉曲之俠，予季次、原憲比權量力，效功於當世，不同日而論矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0020",
          "zh": "要以功見言信，俠客之義又曷可少哉！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0021",
          "zh": "古布衣之俠，靡得而聞已。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0022",
          "zh": "近世延陵、孟嘗、春申、平原、信陵之徒，皆因王者親屬，藉於有土卿相之富厚，招天下賢者，顯名諸侯，不可謂不賢者矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0023",
          "zh": "比如順風而呼，聲非加疾，其埶激也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0024",
          "zh": "至如閭巷之俠，修行砥名，聲施於天下，莫不稱賢，是為難耳。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0025",
          "zh": "然儒、墨皆排擯不載。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0026",
          "zh": "自秦以前，匹夫之俠，湮滅不見，余甚恨之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0027",
          "zh": "以余所聞，漢興有朱家、田仲、王公、劇孟、郭解之徒，雖時捍當世之文罔，然其私義廉絜退讓，有足稱者。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0028",
          "zh": "名不虛立，士不虛附。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0029",
          "zh": "至如朋黨宗彊比周，設財役貧，豪暴侵淩孤弱，恣欲自快，游俠亦丑之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0030",
          "zh": "余悲世俗不察其意，而猥以朱家、郭解等令與暴豪之徒同類而共笑之也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0031",
          "zh": "魯朱家者，與高祖同時。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0032",
          "zh": "魯人皆以儒教，而朱家用俠聞。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0033",
          "zh": "所藏活豪士以百數，其餘庸人不可勝言。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0034",
          "zh": "然終不伐其能，歆其德，諸所嘗施，唯恐見之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0035",
          "zh": "振人不贍，先從貧賤始。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0036",
          "zh": "家無餘財，衣不完采，食不重味，乘不過軥牛。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0037",
          "zh": "專趨人之急，甚己之私。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0038",
          "zh": "既陰脫季布將軍之阸，及布尊貴，終身不見也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0039",
          "zh": "自關以東，莫不延頸願交焉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0040",
          "zh": "楚田仲以俠聞，喜劍，父事朱家，自以為行弗及。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0041",
          "zh": "田仲已死，而雒陽有劇孟。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0042",
          "zh": "周人以商賈為資，而劇孟以任俠顯諸侯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0043",
          "zh": "吳楚反時，條侯為太尉，乘傳車將至河南，得劇孟，喜曰：「吳楚舉大事而不求孟，吾知其無能為已矣。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0044",
          "zh": "天下騷動，宰相得之若得一敵國云。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0045",
          "zh": "劇孟行大類朱家，而好博，多少年之戲。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0046",
          "zh": "然劇孟母死，自遠方送喪蓋千乘。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0047",
          "zh": "及劇孟死，家無餘十金之財。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0048",
          "zh": "而符離人王孟亦以俠稱江淮之閒。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0049",
          "zh": "是時濟南瞷氏、陳周庸亦以豪聞，景帝聞之，使使盡誅此屬。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0050",
          "zh": "其後代諸白、梁韓無辟、陽翟薛兄、陜韓孺紛紛復出焉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0051",
          "zh": "郭解，軹人也，字翁伯，善相人者許負外孫也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0052",
          "zh": "解父以任俠，孝文時誅死。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0053",
          "zh": "解為人短小精悍，不飲酒。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0054",
          "zh": "少時陰賊，慨不快意，身所殺甚眾。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0055",
          "zh": "以軀借交報仇，藏命作姦剽攻，（不）休（及）［乃］鑄錢掘冢，固不可勝數。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0056",
          "zh": "適有天幸，窘急常得脫，若遇赦。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0057",
          "zh": "及解年長，更折節為儉，以德報怨，厚施而薄望。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0058",
          "zh": "然其自喜為俠益甚。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0059",
          "zh": "既已振人之命，不矜其功，其陰賊著於心，卒發於睚金故云。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0060",
          "zh": "而少年慕其行，亦輒為報仇，不使知也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0061",
          "zh": "解姊子負解之勢，與人飲，使之嚼。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0062",
          "zh": "非其任，彊必灌之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0063",
          "zh": "人怒，拔刀刺殺解姊子，亡去。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0064",
          "zh": "解姊怒曰：「以翁伯之義，人殺吾子，賊不得。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0065",
          "zh": "棄其尸於道，弗葬，欲以辱解。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0066",
          "zh": "解使人微知賊處。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0067",
          "zh": "賊窘自歸，具以實告解。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0068",
          "zh": "解曰：「公殺之固當，吾兒不直。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0069",
          "zh": "遂去其賊，罪其姊子，乃收而葬之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0070",
          "zh": "諸公聞之，皆多解之義，益附焉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0071",
          "zh": "解出入，人皆避之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0072",
          "zh": "有一人獨箕倨視之，解遣人問其名姓。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0073",
          "zh": "客欲殺之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0074",
          "zh": "解曰：「居邑屋至不見敬，是吾德不修也，彼何罪！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0075",
          "zh": "乃陰屬尉史曰：「是人，吾所急也，至踐更時脫之。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0076",
          "zh": "每至踐更，數過，吏弗求。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0077",
          "zh": "怪之，問其故，乃解使脫之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0078",
          "zh": "箕踞者乃肉袒謝罪。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0079",
          "zh": "少年聞之，愈益慕解之行。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0080",
          "zh": "雒陽人有相仇者，邑中賢豪居閒者以十數，終不聽。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0081",
          "zh": "客乃見郭解。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0082",
          "zh": "解夜見仇家，仇家曲聽解。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0083",
          "zh": "解乃謂仇家曰：「吾聞雒陽諸公在此閒，多不聽者。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0084",
          "zh": "今子幸而聽解，解柰何乃從他縣奪人邑中賢大夫權乎！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0085",
          "zh": "乃夜去，不使人知，曰：「且無用，（待我）待我去，令雒陽豪居其閒，乃聽之。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0087",
          "zh": "解執恭敬，不敢乘車入其縣廷。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0088",
          "zh": "之旁郡國，為人請求事，事可出，出之；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0089",
          "zh": "不可者，各厭其意，然後乃敢嘗酒食。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0090",
          "zh": "諸公以故嚴重之，爭為用。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0091",
          "zh": "邑中少年及旁近縣賢豪，夜半過門常十餘車，請得解客舍養之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0092",
          "zh": "及徙豪富茂陵也，解家貧，不中訾，吏恐，不敢不徙。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0093",
          "zh": "衛將軍為言：「郭解家貧不中徙。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0094",
          "zh": "上曰：「布衣權至使將軍為言，此其家不貧。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0095",
          "zh": "解家遂徙。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0096",
          "zh": "諸公送者出千餘萬。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0097",
          "zh": "軹人楊季主子為縣掾，舉徙解。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0098",
          "zh": "解兄子斷楊掾頭。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0099",
          "zh": "由此楊氏與郭氏為仇。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0100",
          "zh": "解入關，關中賢豪知與不知，聞其聲，爭交驩解。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0101",
          "zh": "解為人短小，不飲酒，出未嘗有騎。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0102",
          "zh": "已又殺楊季主。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0103",
          "zh": "楊季主家上書，人又殺之闕下。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0104",
          "zh": "上聞，乃下吏捕解。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0105",
          "zh": "解亡，置其母家室夏陽，身至臨晉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0106",
          "zh": "臨晉籍少公素不知解，解冒，因求出關。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0107",
          "zh": "籍少公已出解，解轉入太原，所過輒告主人家。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0108",
          "zh": "吏逐之，跡至籍少公。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0109",
          "zh": "少公自殺，口絕。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0110",
          "zh": "久之，乃得解。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0111",
          "zh": "窮治所犯，為解所殺，皆在赦前。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0112",
          "zh": "軹有儒生侍使者坐，客譽郭解，生曰：「郭解專以姦犯公法，何謂賢！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0113",
          "zh": "解客聞，殺此生，斷其舌。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0114",
          "zh": "吏以此責解，解實不知殺者。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0115",
          "zh": "殺者亦竟絕，莫知為誰。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0116",
          "zh": "吏奏解無罪。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0117",
          "zh": "御史大夫公孫弘議曰：「解布衣為任俠行權，以睚眥殺人，解雖弗知，此罪甚於解殺之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0118",
          "zh": "當大逆無道。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0119",
          "zh": "遂族郭解翁伯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0120",
          "zh": "自是之後，為俠者極眾，敖而無足數者。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0121",
          "zh": "然關中長安樊仲子，槐裏趙王孫，長陵高公子，西河郭公仲，太原鹵公孺，臨淮兒長卿，東陽田君孺，雖為俠而逡逡有退讓君子之風。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0122",
          "zh": "至若北道姚氏，西道諸杜，南道仇景，東道趙他、羽公子，南陽趙調之徒，此盜跖居民閒者耳，曷足道哉！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0123",
          "zh": "此乃鄉者朱家之羞也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0124",
          "zh": "太史公曰：吾視郭解，狀貌不及中人，言語不足採者。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0125",
          "zh": "然天下無賢與不肖，知與不知，皆慕其聲，言俠者皆引以為名。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0126",
          "zh": "諺曰：「人貌榮名，豈有既乎！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0127",
          "zh": "於戲，惜哉！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}